number">1.1.8.</span> <span class="nav-text">上三角行列式</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AF%B9%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.9.</span> <span class="nav-text">对角形行列式</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%B3%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.10.</span> <span class="nav-text">（右下）三角行列式</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-1-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%88%E6%8C%89%E5%88%97%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">1.1 行列式的定义（按列展开）</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-1-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%88%E6%97%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%8C%89%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%8C%89%E5%88%97%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">1.1 行列式的定义（既不按行展开又不按列展开）</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-2-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8"><span class="nav-number">1.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">1.2 行列式的性质</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A81-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%AC%E7%BD%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9B%B8%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%E5%AF%B9%E8%A1%8C%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%AF%B9%E5%88%97%E4%B9%9F%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">性质1 行列式与它的转置行列式相等。对行成立的性质对列也成立。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A82-%E4%BA%92%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%98%E5%8F%B7%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">性质2 互换行列式的两行，行列式变号。</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A83%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E6%AD%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E9%9B%B6%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">推论性质3：如果行列式有两行完全相同，则此行列式等于零。</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A84-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E9%83%BD%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0k%EF%BC%8C%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B0k%E4%B9%98%E6%AD%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">性质4 行列式的某一行中所有的元素都乘以同一个数k，等于用数k乘此行列式。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A85%EF%BC%9A%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%A0%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%8A%E5%9B%A0%E5%AD%90%E6%8F%90%E5%88%B0%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">推论性质5：行列式中如果有一行有公因子，则可以把因子提到行列式外面。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A85-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E6%88%90%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E6%AD%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E9%9B%B6%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">性质5 行列式中如果有两行元素成比例，则此行列式等于零。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E0%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E0%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">推论：某一行全等于0，行列式等于0。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A86-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%A4%E6%95%B0%E4%B9%8B%E5%92%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E6%8B%86%E6%88%90%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E3%80%82%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%AA%E6%8B%86%E5%88%86%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.4.7.</span> <span class="nav-text">性质6 行列式的某一行，所有元素都是两数之和，可以把行列式拆成两个行列式的和。（只拆分那一行）</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A87-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%AD%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%8E%BB%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%98%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.4.8.</span> <span class="nav-text">性质7 行列式中某一行乘以一个数加到另一行去，行列式不变。</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-3-%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E6%8C%89%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80"><span class="nav-number">1.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">1.3 行列式按行展开</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-3-1-%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%99%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">1.5.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">1.3.1 代数余子式</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%BD%99%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">1.5.1.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">余子式</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%99%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">1.5.1.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">代数余子式</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E6%8C%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%88%96%E5%88%97%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%EF%BC%88%E9%99%8D%E9%98%B6%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.5.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">行列式按行或列展开（降阶）</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%8C%89%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80"><span class="nav-number">1.5.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">按行展开</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%8C%89%E5%88%97%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80"><span class="nav-number">1.5.2.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">按列展开</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%BC%82%E4%B9%98%E5%8F%98%E9%9B%B6%E5%AE%9A%E7%90%86"><span class="nav-number">1.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">异乘变零定理</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%8B%89%E6%99%AE%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E5%AE%9A%E7%90%86"><span class="nav-number">1.7.</span> <span class="nav-text">拉普拉斯定理</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#k%E9%98%B6%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">1.7.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">k阶子式</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%BD%99%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%8F-1"><span class="nav-number">1.7.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">余子式</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-5-3-%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%99%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">1.7.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">1.5.3 代数余子式</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-5-4-%E6%8B%89%E6%99%AE%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E5%AE%9A%E7%90%86"><span class="nav-number">1.7.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">1.5.4 拉普拉斯定理</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#1-5-5-%E5%90%8C%E9%98%B6%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E5%BC%8F%E7%9B%B8%E4%